This is the cover of a program for a concert by the Fisk University Choir of sixty voices, at Carnegie Hall, Thursday January 26th, for a program of negro spirituals directed by guest conductor Dr. T. Tertius Noble, and Ray Francis Brown, director of the choir, director of the Fisk Department of Music.
